[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">The following is a record of what</st> <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02518\" class=\"\">Hilkiah</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">prophesied</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> He was <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">one of</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> lived at <st data-num=\"06068\" class=\"\">Anathoth</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">territory</st> of the tribe of <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him<n id=\"2\" /> in the <st data-num=\"07969 06240\">thirteenth</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> that <st data-num=\"02977\" class=\"\">Josiah</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0526\" class=\"\">Amon</st> <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">ruled over</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "It also <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> in the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> of <st data-num=\"03079\" class=\"\">Jehoiakim</st>, <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02977\" class=\"\">Josiah</st>, <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, and continued <st data-num=\"05704 08552\">until</st> the <st data-num=\"06249 06240\">eleventh</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">year</st> of <st data-num=\"06667\" class=\"\">Zedekiah</st>, <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02977\" class=\"\">Josiah</st>, <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> the people of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"1\" /> were <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">taken into exile</st> in the <st data-num=\"02549\">fifth</st> <st data-num=\"02320\">month</st> of that year.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me,</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02962\" class=\"\">Before</st> I <st data-num=\"03335\" class=\"\">formed</st> you in your mother\u2019s <st data-num=\"0990\" class=\"\">womb</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">chose</st> you.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02962\" class=\"\">Before</st> you were <st data-num=\"03318 07358\">born</st>, I <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">set</st> you <st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">apart</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">appointed</st> you to be a <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> to the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">answered</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0162\" class=\"\">Oh</st>, <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Really</st><n id=\"2\" /> I do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know how</st> to <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">speak</st> well enough for that,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am too <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, \u201cDo <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am too <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">young</st>.\u2019 <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">whomever</st> I <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> you and <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">say</st> <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">whatever</st> I <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">tell</st> you.",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">of</st> those to whom I send you,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will be <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> you to <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">protect</st><n id=\"2\" /> you,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">reached out</st> his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> and <st data-num=\"05060 05921\">touched</st> my <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st> and <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, \u201cI will <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">most assuredly</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">give</st> you the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> you are to <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">speak</st> for me.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">Know for certain that</st><n id=\"1\" /> I <st data-num=\"03117 02088\">hereby</st> <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">give</st> you <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">the authority</st> to announce <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> and <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdoms</st> that they will be<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05428\" class=\"\">uprooted</st> and <st data-num=\"05422\" class=\"\">torn down</st>, <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> and <st data-num=\"02040\" class=\"\">demolished</st>, <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">rebuilt</st> and <st data-num=\"05193\" class=\"\">firmly planted</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Later</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\">to</st> me, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> do <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st>, <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st>?\u201d I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">answered</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> a <st data-num=\"04731\" class=\"\">branch</st> of an <st data-num=\"08247\" class=\"\">almond tree</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "Then the <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\"><span class=\"\"smcaps\"\">Lord</span></st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">said</st>, \u201cYou have <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">observed</st> <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">correctly</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">This means</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> am <st data-num=\"08245\" class=\"\">watching</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to make sure</st> my <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">threats</st> are <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">carried out</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me a <st data-num=\"08145\" class=\"\">second</st> time, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> do <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st>?\u201d I <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">answered</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> a <st data-num=\"05518\" class=\"\">pot</st> of <st data-num=\"05301\" class=\"\">boiling water</st>; it is <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">tipped</st> <st data-num=\"06440\">away from</st> the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">said</st>, \u201cFrom the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07451\">destruction</st> will <st data-num=\"06605\">break out</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>. ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I will <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">soon</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summon</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04940\" class=\"\">peoples</st> of the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdoms</st> of the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. \u201cThey will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> and their <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">kings</st> will <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">set up</st> their <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">thrones</st><n id=\"1\" /> near the <st data-num=\"06607\" class=\"\">entrances</st> of the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gates</st> of <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> They will <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">attack</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">walls</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">surrounding</st> it and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> in <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "In this way<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">pass</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">sentence</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">on</st> the people of Jerusalem and Judah<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because of</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> their <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wickedness</st>. <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">For</st> they <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">rejected</st> me and <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">offered sacrifices</st> to <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">other</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>, <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiping</st> <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">what</st> they <st data-num=\"04639\" class=\"\">made</st> with their own <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hands</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201cBut <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, Jeremiah,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0247 04975\">get</st> yourself <st data-num=\"0247 04975\">ready</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Go</st> and <st data-num=\"01696 0413\">tell</st> these people <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">everything</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">instruct</st> you to say. Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">be terrified</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">of</st> them, <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">or</st> I will <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">give</st> you <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">good reason to be terrified</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">of</st> them.<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">hereby</st> <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">promise</st> to <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> you<n id=\"2\" /> as strong as a <st data-num=\"04013\" class=\"\">fortified</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st>, an <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st> <st data-num=\"05982\" class=\"\">pillar</st>, and a <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st> <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">wall</st>. You will be able to stand up <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> who live in<n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>, including the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">kings</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>, its <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st>, its <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>, and all the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.  ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "1",
    "text": "They will <st data-num=\"03898 0413\">attack</st> you but they will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">be able to overcome</st> you, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will be <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> you to <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">rescue</st> you,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  }
]